12.000Z","msg":"香港大把錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/daily/article/20180325/20342382\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180325%2F20342382&d=n9v%2FnEhgMshiD86tyvOXgAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=f5c637bd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180325%2F20342382&h=2ae4e708\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/daily/article/20180325/20342382</a><br />\n其實小市民不是擔心走資，而是港元滙價一日不到7.85，金管局一日都不出手，齊齊睇住香港資產泡沫變大而無能為力。又話說白頭任去年9月攞過彩，說金管局只要發行外滙基金票據吸引市場流動性，便毋須等港滙7.85才出手那樣被動，潛台詞是趁泡沫未爆前做定工夫，其實也無可厚非。奈何不知攞命陳鬥氣還是夠薑，對外重申只會到7.85才出手。"},{"pid":"791234cc02e3659b9e549b6a01ee68745e46cb34","tid":610433,"uid":169074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T03:53:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8e132d53696ca318a9af37b578d60fb29d7e3405","tid":610433,"uid":45518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T03:57:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5b6e0f48022b2a5b92a4aca31c5ab86c832af51","tid":610433,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T04:05:59.000Z","msg":"加息囉 追加囉"},{"pid":"657da73f5e025a82150922ea339ff79024a1ecd5","tid":610433,"uid":174649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T23:57:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a5fdfc4996a5a0f61f5c03d893b38f523560322","tid":610433,"uid":174649,"like":